    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require cctv inside graveyards",
        "additional_details": "It is despicable how many of these souls are not being allowed to rest whether its breaking headstone\u2019s ,trashing them up ,cutting flowers, bike\u2019s and cars going through leaving tyre marks. No one wants to go to a loved ones grave to see anything bad on it or done to it thats where people are to rest and not everyone treats it like that and these families deserve justice.",
        "background": "We believe we need cctv inside graveyards because so many families have to go through vandalism of graves inside graveyards. ",
